results.title: A resolution commending the Northwest Missouri State University Bearcats on their National Collegiate Athletic Association Division II national championship victories.
results.short_title: A resolution commending the Northwest Missouri State University Bearcats on their National Collegiate Athletic Association Division II national championship victories.
results.latest_major_action: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Unanimous Consent. (consideration: CR S2728; text: CR S2725; sponsor introductory remarks on measure: CR S2726)
results.summary: (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Commends the Northwest Missouri State University Bearcats for their Division II national championship victories in football and men's basketball.
results.summary_short: (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Commends the Northwest Missouri State University Bearcats for their Division II national championship victories in football and men's basketball.
